the jewel and the heart

00:34:12.489 --> 00:34:15.730 align:middle line:84%
of the golden lotus, which
is the Chintamani Stone,

00:34:15.730 --> 00:34:19.080 align:middle line:90%
and chant om mani padme hum.

00:34:19.080 --> 00:34:21.239 align:middle line:90%
Om mani padme hum.

00:34:21.239 --> 00:34:23.030 align:middle line:84%
So here we are
once again linking

00:34:23.030 --> 00:34:27.540 align:middle line:84%
the idea of sound or
vibration with the stone.

00:34:27.540 --> 00:34:30.560 align:middle line:84%
The jewel or stone
which is the Chintamani

00:34:30.560 --> 00:34:34.429 align:middle line:84%
is also called the blue pearl,
as I noted a moment ago.

00:34:34.429 --> 00:34:36.920 align:middle line:84%
So in Buddhist art we will
see the awakened ones,

00:34:36.920 --> 00:34:40.500 align:middle line:84%
the Bodhisattvas, in this
radiant portal or gateway

00:34:40.500 --> 00:34:44.429 align:middle line:84%
holding the blue pearl
or the Chintamani Stone.

00:34:44.429 --> 00:34:46.730 align:middle line:84%
The goal of meditation
in the Siddha practice

00:34:46.730 --> 00:34:50.760 align:middle line:84%
is to see this blue
pearl or this blue stone

00:34:50.760 --> 00:34:55.052 align:middle line:84%
and ultimately to go inside
it and to merge with it.

00:34:55.052 --> 00:34:56.800 align:middle line:84%
Within the blue
pearl or stone you

00:34:56.800 --> 00:34:58.770 align:middle line:84%
will see the deity you
have personal devotion

00:34:58.770 --> 00:35:04.520 align:middle line:84%
to, be it Ptah, Jesus, Buddha,
Sai Baba, Krishna, or Rama.

00:35:04.520 --> 00:35:07.490 align:middle line:84%
So here we are once
again holding the stone

00:35:07.490 --> 00:35:10.820 align:middle line:84%
with the open portal
or gateway behind us.

00:35:10.820 --> 00:35:13.960 align:middle line:84%
And this is, again, what we
see in Christian ascension art.

00:35:13.960 --> 00:35:18.590 align:middle line:84%
Jesus is ascending through
the blue portal or gateway,

00:35:18.590 --> 00:35:22.290 align:middle line:84%
indicating that he's traveling
into the divine realms.

00:35:22.290 --> 00:35:25.880 align:middle line:84%
And it could well be that
this blue orb he's riding on

00:35:25.880 --> 00:35:30.030 align:middle line:84%
is a Christian symbol
for the Chintamani Stone.

00:35:30.030 --> 00:35:31.980 align:middle line:84%
It's very interesting
to me that Jesus

00:35:31.980 --> 00:35:35.300 align:middle line:84%
holds the ring of
sovereignty in his hand

00:35:35.300 --> 00:35:37.520 align:middle line:90%
as well as a rolled up scroll.

00:35:37.520 --> 00:35:42.740 align:middle line:84%
So the ring unites us once again
with the stone and the scroll

00:35:42.740 --> 00:35:44.655 align:middle line:84%
in a way could be
thought of actually

00:35:44.655 --> 00:35:48.670 align:middle line:90%
as the rod or the wand.

00:35:48.670 --> 00:35:50.580 align:middle line:84%
In this beautiful
alchemical depiction

00:35:50.580 --> 00:35:53.680 align:middle line:84%
from the Divine Comedy
by Giovanni de Paolo

00:35:53.680 --> 00:35:57.360 align:middle line:84%
we see Jesus in the
blue orb surrounded

00:35:57.360 --> 00:36:01.266 align:middle line:84%
by the ouroboros, the symbol
of the alchemical craft.

00:36:01.266 --> 00:36:03.140 align:middle line:84%
So we know that what
we're talking about here

00:36:03.140 --> 00:36:08.120 align:middle line:84%
is that divine magic or
theurgy that Marsilio Ficino

00:36:08.120 --> 00:36:11.230 align:middle line:84%
spoke of and wrote so
passionately about.

00:36:11.230 --> 00:36:14.710 align:middle line:84%
And view Jesus, once
again, as the exemplar

00:36:14.710 --> 00:36:18.490 align:middle line:84%
of the ultimate human potential
to transform ourselves

00:36:18.490 --> 00:36:24.340 align:middle line:84%
into rainbow body light beings
and ascend into the heavenly

00:36:24.340 --> 00:36:25.840 align:middle line:90%
realms.

00:36:25.840 --> 00:36:27.960 align:middle line:84%
So a few more
examples here of Jesus

00:36:27.960 --> 00:36:32.380 align:middle line:84%
ascending or transforming
with the open blue portal

00:36:32.380 --> 00:36:34.580 align:middle line:90%
or gateway behind him.

00:36:34.580 --> 00:36:37.690 align:middle line:84%
This one here from Egypt
in the 10th century where

00:36:37.690 --> 00:36:42.240 align:middle line:84%
we see Jesus on the throne
with the blue rings behind him.

00:36:42.240 --> 00:36:44.610 align:middle line:84%
And when we see concentric
rings in a painting,

00:36:44.610 --> 00:36:47.050 align:middle line:84%
we have to remember
it almost always can

00:36:47.050 --> 00:36:52.940 align:middle line:84%
indicate sound or vibration as
