00:36:52.940 --> 00:36:53.910 align:middle line:90%
a vortex.

00:36:53.910 --> 00:36:58.710 align:middle line:84%
So once again, we're uniting the
idea of ascension with a portal

00:36:58.710 --> 00:37:00.800 align:middle line:90%
and also with sound.

00:37:00.800 --> 00:37:03.090 align:middle line:84%
From the Hagio
Sofia we see Jesus

00:37:03.090 --> 00:37:07.110 align:middle line:84%
in the blue orb of concentric
rings filled with manna or star

00:37:07.110 --> 00:37:08.740 align:middle line:84%
stuff descending
into the heavens.

00:37:08.740 --> 00:37:13.320 align:middle line:90%


00:37:13.320 --> 00:37:15.830 align:middle line:84%
Jerusalem's Dome of
the Rock is described

00:37:15.830 --> 00:37:20.160 align:middle line:84%
as an x place or a portal
or a stargate where

00:37:20.160 --> 00:37:22.614 align:middle line:84%
the heavenly fire
meets the earth.

00:37:22.614 --> 00:37:24.030 align:middle line:84%
And I thought it
would be valuable

00:37:24.030 --> 00:37:26.790 align:middle line:84%
for us to take a moment
to go inside this most

00:37:26.790 --> 00:37:29.140 align:middle line:84%
sacred dot of real
estate on earth

00:37:29.140 --> 00:37:32.100 align:middle line:84%
and appreciate its
portal symbolism.

00:37:32.100 --> 00:37:35.150 align:middle line:84%
There's another reason we want
to look into this sacred place.

00:37:35.150 --> 00:37:37.820 align:middle line:84%
And that is because
this location

00:37:37.820 --> 00:37:42.330 align:middle line:84%
is marked by one of the most
profound locations on earth.

00:37:42.330 --> 00:37:44.260 align:middle line:84%
The Dome of the
Rock conceals what

00:37:44.260 --> 00:37:48.060 align:middle line:84%
is considered to be the
most sacred stone or rock

00:37:48.060 --> 00:37:50.410 align:middle line:90%
and dot of real estate on earth.

00:37:50.410 --> 00:37:52.880 align:middle line:84%
It is called the
Foundation Stone

00:37:52.880 --> 00:37:54.740 align:middle line:84%
and is said to have
been planted here

00:37:54.740 --> 00:37:57.280 align:middle line:84%
at the beginning of
creation and taken

00:37:57.280 --> 00:38:00.060 align:middle line:90%
by God from his throne of glory.

00:38:00.060 --> 00:38:01.760 align:middle line:84%
Jews see it as the
center of the Earth,

00:38:01.760 --> 00:38:05.280 align:middle line:84%
the axis of the universe, the
ladder or stairway to heaven,

00:38:05.280 --> 00:38:08.210 align:middle line:84%
the connecting link that
joins heaven and earth,

00:38:08.210 --> 00:38:11.980 align:middle line:84%
or the pivot that
joins heaven and earth.

00:38:11.980 --> 00:38:16.440 align:middle line:84%
And here is a beautiful painting
showing that Foundation Stone,

00:38:16.440 --> 00:38:18.540 align:middle line:84%
the most sacred dot of
real estate on earth,

00:38:18.540 --> 00:38:21.830 align:middle line:84%
according to the Judeo
Christian tradition.

00:38:21.830 --> 00:38:24.600 align:middle line:84%
And here is a modern day
photograph showing the stone

00:38:24.600 --> 00:38:27.740 align:middle line:84%
with the portal imagery
above it on the interior

00:38:27.740 --> 00:38:29.610 align:middle line:90%
of the Dome of the Rock.

00:38:29.610 --> 00:38:32.180 align:middle line:84%
This of course is
the location where

00:38:32.180 --> 00:38:35.580 align:middle line:84%
the Jews had taken the
Ark of the Covenant.

00:38:35.580 --> 00:38:37.880 align:middle line:84%
And it was also the location
of Solomon's temple,

00:38:37.880 --> 00:38:40.750 align:middle line:84%
the permanent home
for the Ark, which

00:38:40.750 --> 00:38:44.460 align:middle line:84%
was housed in the holy of
holies of Solomon's temple.

00:38:44.460 --> 00:38:47.830 align:middle line:84%
And inside the holy of holies
was the most holy place,

00:38:47.830 --> 00:38:51.600 align:middle line:84%
this golden cube shaped room
where the Ark of the Covenant

00:38:51.600 --> 00:38:53.260 align:middle line:90%
was located.

00:38:53.260 --> 00:38:55.600 align:middle line:84%
And here we see the
Israelite priests

00:38:55.600 --> 00:38:58.420 align:middle line:84%
carrying the Ark of the
Covenant in the wilderness,

00:38:58.420 --> 00:39:02.030 align:middle line:84%
ultimately taking it to its
destination in Jerusalem.

00:39:02.030 --> 00:39:04.620 align:middle line:84%
And we see the divine
pillar emanating

00:39:04.620 --> 00:39:07.910 align:middle line:84%
from the Ark of the Covenant,
indicating its purpose, which

00:39:07.910 --> 00:39:11.390 align:middle line:90%
is to link heaven and earth.

00:39:11.390 --> 00:39:13.800 align:middle line:84%
What most don't realize is
that the Ark of the Covenant

00:39:13.800 --> 00:39:18.340 align:middle line:84%
was considered to be the throne
of the Israelite God Yahweh.

00:39:18.340 --> 00:39:20.800 align:middle line:84%
And in the Bible,
Yahweh is described

00:39:20.800 --> 00:39:25.800 align:middle line:84%
as a luminous humanoid figure
with a rainbow-like energy

00:39:25.800 --> 00:39:26.950 align:middle line:90%
around him.

00:39:26.950 --> 00:39:31.780 align:middle line:84%
He's luminous, humanoid, and
surrounded in rainbow light.

00:39:31.780 --> 00:39:34.600 align:middle line:84%
And that's powerful because
it raises the question

00:39:34.600 --> 00:39:39.080 align:middle line:84%
or possibility that in fact
Yahweh was a rainbow body

00:39:39.080 --> 00:39:43.020 align:middle line:84%
being, which is very, very
strong statement to make,

00:39:43.020 --> 00:39:45.300 align:middle line:84%
but also tremendously
controversial

00:39:45.300 --> 00:39:47.740 align:middle line:84%
because most don't think
of the Old Testament God

00:39:47.740 --> 00:39:50.590 align:middle line:90%
as being a humanoid figure.

00:39:50.590 --> 00:39:52.270 align:middle line:84%
And what we notice
in this painting

00:39:52.270 --> 00:39:55.520 align:middle line:84%
by Carl Gutherz in the Library
of Congress reading room

00:39:55.520 --> 00:40:01.140 align:middle line:84%
is that Yahweh on his throne
holds a stone in his hand.

00:40:01.140 --> 00:40:06.360 align:middle line:84%
And this stone is remarkably
similar in its symbolism

00:40:06.360 --> 00:40:08.800 align:middle line:84%
and appearance and also
perhaps its purpose

00:40:08.800 --> 00:40:11.650 align:middle line:90%
to the Chintamani Stone.

00:40:11.650 --> 00:40:15.460 align:middle line:84%
Is it possible that we are
seeing yet another connection

00:40:15.460 --> 00:40:18.780 align:middle line:84%
between the Buddhist
Bodhisattvas and the Old

00:40:18.780 --> 00:40:20.900 align:middle line:90%
Testament God Yahweh?

00:40:20.900 --> 00:40:22.550 align:middle line:84%
We know that the
Ark of the Covenant

00:40:22.550 --> 00:40:27.950 align:middle line:84%
is the device upon which he sits
and it held several other tools

00:40:27.950 --> 00:40:31.260 align:middle line:84%
or instruments, including
the rod of Aaron,

00:40:31.260 --> 00:40:35.650 align:middle line:84%
the rod of enlightenment,
the tablet or stones

00:40:35.650 --> 00:40:37.660 align:middle line:84%
that had the Ten
Commandments written on them,

00:40:37.660 --> 00:40:41.490 align:middle line:84%
a flask of manna as well
as a cruc of sacred oil.

00:40:41.490 --> 00:40:43.430 align:middle line:84%
So once again,
it's very possible

00:40:43.430 --> 00:40:46.450 align:middle line:84%
that the stone in Yahweh's
hand and the stone

00:40:46.450 --> 00:40:51.270 align:middle line:84%
