the same thing, the Chintamani

00:40:51.270 --> 00:40:54.516 align:middle line:84%
stone, the wish
fulfilling jewel.

00:40:54.516 --> 00:40:57.700 align:middle line:84%
But we're going to take
this one layer deeper.

00:40:57.700 --> 00:41:01.250 align:middle line:84%
Because we know from Buddhist
teachings as well as Christian

00:41:01.250 --> 00:41:04.060 align:middle line:84%
teachings that all
of this actually

00:41:04.060 --> 00:41:06.730 align:middle line:90%
happens inside our bodies.

00:41:06.730 --> 00:41:09.970 align:middle line:84%
And whether it's Jesus holding
the stone in his hand here as

00:41:09.970 --> 00:41:13.560 align:middle line:84%
he's doing in this
painting by Fra Angelico,

00:41:13.560 --> 00:41:16.410 align:middle line:84%
or it's Jesus in
this example here

00:41:16.410 --> 00:41:20.150 align:middle line:84%
on his heavenly throne where
he's holding the stone,

00:41:20.150 --> 00:41:22.860 align:middle line:84%
or in this example
here as a child where

00:41:22.860 --> 00:41:24.830 align:middle line:84%
he's holding the
stone, which symbolizes

00:41:24.830 --> 00:41:27.580 align:middle line:84%
universal power,
that all of these

00:41:27.580 --> 00:41:30.860 align:middle line:84%
represent something that
happens inside of us.

00:41:30.860 --> 00:41:33.460 align:middle line:84%
In "Foundation Stone and
Jerusalem of the Mind,"

00:41:33.460 --> 00:41:36.110 align:middle line:84%
author JD Bakst notes
that one of the names

00:41:36.110 --> 00:41:39.340 align:middle line:84%
of the pineal gland in the
center of the brain which

00:41:39.340 --> 00:41:43.260 align:middle line:84%
