00:41:43.260 --> 00:41:45.240 align:middle line:90%
is the foundation stone.

00:41:45.240 --> 00:41:47.310 align:middle line:84%
This gland has long
been considered

00:41:47.310 --> 00:41:52.360 align:middle line:84%
