They theorize that
the interactions

00:42:22.250 --> 00:42:24.390 align:middle line:84%
of these crystals
with global system

00:42:24.390 --> 00:42:26.600 align:middle line:84%
for mobile
telecommunication waves

00:42:26.600 --> 00:42:30.680 align:middle line:84%
could constitute a new
mechanism of transduction

00:42:30.680 --> 00:42:31.960 align:middle line:90%
of the perennial membrane.

00:42:31.960 --> 00:42:34.080 align:middle line:84%
What this means
in layman's terms

00:42:34.080 --> 00:42:37.010 align:middle line:84%
is that our pineal
gland is a cell phone.

